flowchart TD
    START((Incident Detected)) --> A[Log incident in system]
    A --> B[Initial triage and severity]
    B --> SEV{Severity?}
    SEV --> P1[P1 - Critical]
    SEV --> P2[P2 - High]
    SEV --> P3[P3 - Medium]
    SEV --> P4[P4 - Low]
    P1 --> NOTIFY
    P2 --> NOTIFY
    P3 --> NOTIFY
    P4 --> NOTIFY
    NOTIFY[Notify stakeholders per severity SLA]
    NOTIFY --> C[Coordinate with vendor]
    C --> D[Assess impact to our data/operations]
    D --> E{Our data affected?}
    E -->|Yes| F[Activate internal IR process]
    F --> G
    E -->|No| G[Monitor vendor remediation]
    G --> H[Post-incident review]
    H --> I[Update risk assessment]
    I --> J{Continue vendor?}
    J -->|No| K[Initiate offboarding]
    K --> END1((End))
    J -->|Yes| L[Update controls and monitoring]
    L --> END2((Complete))
